Touch Optimized: Features a minimum of 48px touch targets to ensure ease of use and prevent accidental clicks.

High Contrast: Deep blacks and vibrant blues ensure clear visibility in dark mode environments.

Floating Action Button (FAB): A prominent, glowing blue "+" button sits in the center of the navigation bar for primary actions (likely "Create Group" or "Add Funds").
